1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,970
[Episode 52]

2
00:00:06,270 --> 00:00:07,070
Let me ask you.

3
00:00:08,310 --> 00:00:09,510
When did you find out?

4
00:00:09,830 --> 00:00:10,750
Who I am.

5
00:00:12,350 --> 00:00:13,480
From the first time.

6
00:00:16,309 --> 00:00:17,640
When we slept together.

7
00:00:18,230 --> 00:00:19,270
Are you saying

8
00:00:21,670 --> 00:00:22,910
that everything was

9
00:00:22,910 --> 00:00:24,110
your revenge, right?

10
00:00:26,150 --> 00:00:26,510
Yes.

11
00:00:29,630 --> 00:00:30,550
I hate you.

12
00:00:32,590 --> 00:00:34,250
I hate that fat guy from Class 1

13
00:00:35,230 --> 00:00:37,430
who said my appearance was disgusting,

14
00:00:37,590 --> 00:00:39,390
just like my promiscuous heart.

15
00:00:39,750 --> 00:00:40,470
So

16
00:00:41,710 --> 00:00:43,640
I wanted to make him look like a fool

17
00:00:44,630 --> 00:00:47,890
-for getting involved
-with someone as promiscuous as me.

18
00:01:04,470 --> 00:01:05,230
So you mean

19
00:01:07,590 --> 00:01:08,050
that...

20
00:01:09,270 --> 00:01:10,600
Everything in the past,

21
00:01:13,789 --> 00:01:15,650
all those things we did together,

22
00:01:16,510 --> 00:01:18,039
you never loved me, did you?

23
00:01:20,230 --> 00:01:21,030
That's right.

24
00:01:22,830 --> 00:01:24,030
I never loved you.

25
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:28,190
How does it feel

26
00:01:29,550 --> 00:01:31,310
to be betrayed?

27
00:01:33,030 --> 00:01:34,430
Quite painful, isn't it?

28
00:01:43,710 --> 00:01:44,990
You hate me because of what happened eight years ago,

29
00:01:44,990 --> 00:01:45,710
don't you?

30
00:01:50,430 --> 00:01:51,190
So you knew.

31
00:01:56,390 --> 00:01:56,990
Yes.

32
00:02:00,910 --> 00:02:01,970
I've always known.

33
00:02:03,310 --> 00:02:04,230
I know

34
00:02:05,670 --> 00:02:06,870
you're the one I love,

35
00:02:10,070 --> 00:02:10,800
love deeply,

36
00:02:15,190 --> 00:02:16,590
and also hate intensely.

37
00:02:21,630 --> 00:02:22,750
Now you know,

38
00:02:23,950 --> 00:02:25,310
attractive people

39
00:02:27,390 --> 00:02:28,450
can be just as wild.

40
00:02:31,910 --> 00:02:32,710
Fine.

41
00:02:36,310 --> 00:02:38,310
I'll personally fill

42
00:02:38,310 --> 00:02:39,640
your dissatisfaction.

43
00:02:43,390 --> 00:02:44,450
What are you doing?

44
00:02:47,790 --> 00:02:50,250
-I'll never say
-anything nice to you again.

45
00:02:51,350 --> 00:02:52,430
Are you crazy?

46
00:02:55,430 --> 00:02:56,560
Let's end this here.

47
00:02:57,810 --> 00:03:00,290
[To Be Continued]
